                    Posted in <a href="http://ereads.com/category/all" title="View all posts in All" rel="category tag">All</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/copyright-and-piracy" title="View all posts in Copyright and Piracy" rel="category tag">Copyright and Piracy</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-book-reader-technology" title="View all posts in E-Book Reader Technology" rel="category tag">E-Book Reader Technology</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-book-industry-news" title="View all posts in E-book Industry (news)" rel="category tag">E-book Industry (news)</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-books-business" title="View all posts in E-books (business)" rel="category tag">E-books (business)</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/publishing-industry-2" title="View all posts in Publishing Industry" rel="category tag">Publishing Industry</a> <strong>|</strong> <a href="http://ereads.com/2010/12/uncle-sam-cracks-down-on-music-and-movie-piracy-but-books-nope.html#comments" title="Comment on Uncle Sam Cracks Down on Music and Movie Piracy. But What&#8217;s with Books?">1 Comment &#187;</a>  
                    
