                     Tags: <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/adsense" rel="tag">AdSense</a>, <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/advertising" rel="tag">Advertising</a>, <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/google" rel="tag">Google</a>, <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/google-ebooks" rel="tag">Google eBooks</a><br> 
                    Posted in <a href="http://ereads.com/category/all" title="View all posts in All" rel="category tag">All</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-book-reader-technology" title="View all posts in E-Book Reader Technology" rel="category tag">E-Book Reader Technology</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-book-applications" title="View all posts in E-book Applications" rel="category tag">E-book Applications</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-book-industry-news" title="View all posts in E-book Industry (news)" rel="category tag">E-book Industry (news)</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/e-books-business" title="View all posts in E-books (business)" rel="category tag">E-books (business)</a> <strong>|</strong> <a href="http://ereads.com/2010/12/ads-on-google-ebooks-it-will-happen-says-forrester.html#comments" title="Comment on Ads on Google eBooks? &#8220;It Will Happen&#8221; says Forrester">2 Comment &#187;</a>  
                    
