                     Tags: <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/dorchester-books" rel="tag">Dorchester Books</a>, <a href="http://ereads.com/tag/science-fiction-writers-of-america" rel="tag">Science Fiction Writers of America</a><br> 
                    Posted in <a href="http://ereads.com/category/advice-for-writers" title="View all posts in Advice for Writers" rel="category tag">Advice for Writers</a>,  <a href="http://ereads.com/category/publishing-industry-2" title="View all posts in Publishing Industry" rel="category tag">Publishing Industry</a> <strong>|</strong> <a href="http://ereads.com/2010/12/sfwa-gives-dorchester-a-second-chance.html#respond" title="Comment on SFWA Puts Dorchester on Probation">0 Comments &#187;</a>  
                    
